Class Bp723Control

    DeviceControl

    public class Bp723Control
extends Bp926Control
implements DeviceControl
    Public API for the KD723

    The class provides methods to control KD723 device. You need to call the device method, and then call the connection method

    If you want to connect a KD926 device, you need to calliHealthDevicesManager.startDiscovery(long) to discovery a new KD723 device, and then calliHealthDevicesManager.connectDevice(java.lang.String, java.lang.String)to connect KD723 device.
